'''Raymond T McNally''' (1931&ndash;2002) was an American author and a professor of Russian and East European History at [[Boston College]].  He specialized in the history of horror and wrote many books on the subject. He co-authored several books with [[Radu Florescu]] (1925&ndash;2014), who was also a professor at Boston College.

